dback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ikn1665702918024.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ikn1665702918024.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ikn1665702918024.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ikn1665702918024\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Convert from meta to an external character set.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__topic_d131066e1_d131067e1_d131068e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131069e1_d131070e1_d131071e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">long ucnvext(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">uctrl</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">src</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">dst</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">max</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131072e1_d131073e1_d131074e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">struct uctrl</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">*uctrl</var>;</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131075e1_d131076e1_d131077e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">unsigned char</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">*src</var>;</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131078e1_d131079e1_d131080e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">unsigned char</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">*dst</var>;</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131081e1_d131082e1_d131083e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">int</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">max</var>;</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__section_tys_wns_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1162602e120\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__parml_twy_xns_gwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">uctrl</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Uniface I/O control block.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">src</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Pointer to the source buffer to convert.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">dst</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Pointer to the destination buffer.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">max</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Maximum number of bytes to write to the destination.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__section_iyy_b4s_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1162602e169\">Return values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131090e1_d131091e1_d131092e1\">The number of bytes to the destination or when the\n            destination was not large enough, the return value will be negative. The value still\n            indicates the number of bytes to the destination.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__section_snc_lnz_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1162602e178\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Convert from meta to an external character set.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131099e1_d131100e1_d131101e1\">The destination buffer will be null-terminated.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131102e1_d131103e1_d131104e1\">When the destination byte limit (maximum) equals\n            zero, the destination is assumed large enough to always contain all converted source\n            data.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131105e1_d131106e1_d131107e1\">Partial conversion will always result in valid\n            output, the end of the destination will always contain a complete character.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikn1665702918024__p_d131108e1_d131109e1_d131110e1\">For more information, see the \"Double-Byte\n            Character Strings\" topic.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dvo1665702978597.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Double-Byte Character Strings</a><p>Multibyte character sets are available for use with Uniface. Only connectors for databases that support double-byte data need to be changed.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528586\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528586\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ucnvext Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Convert from meta to an external character set. long ucnvext( uctrl , src , dst , max ) struct uctrl *uctrl ; unsigned char *src ; unsigned char *dst ; int max ; Parameters uctrl Uniface I/O control block. src Pointer to the source buffer to convert. dst Pointer to the destination buffer. max Maximum number of bytes to write to the destination. Return values The number of bytes to the destination or when the destination was not large enough, the return value will be negative. The value still indicates the number of bytes to the destination. Description Convert from meta to an external character set. The destination buffer will be null-terminated. When the destination byte limit (maximum) equals zero, the destination is assumed large enough to always contain all converted source data. Partial conversion will always result in valid output, the end of the destination will always contain a complete character. For more information, see the \"Double-Byte Character Strings\" topic. Related Links Double-Byte Character Strings Multibyte character sets are available for use with Uniface. Only connectors for databases that support double-byte data need to be changed. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}